---
import Image from "../assets/fotito.png";
import Curriculum from "../assets/CV-JM.pdf";
---

<header class="max-w-[calc(990px+4rem)] flex flex-col-reverse flex-wrap p-8 gap-20 justify-center items-center min-h-[calc(70vh-5rem-2px-6rem)] md:flex-row">
    <div class="flex flex-col text-center md:flex-1 md:text-start">
        <span class='hidden md:block'>Hola!</span>
        <h1 class='text-5xl font-semibold'>Me llamo <span class='bg-gradient-to-r to-[#1237f6] from-[#09f4f4] text-gradient'>Joel</span>.</h1>
        <p class='text-4xl'>Desarrollador Junior.</p>
        <p class='my-4'>
            Soy egresado de la carrera de Ing. de software. 
            Mi objetivo es seguir creciendo en mi carrera como ingeniero de software y
            desarrollar soluciones innovadoras que impulsen la tecnolog√≠a.
        </p>
        <div class='flex gap-3 items-center h-12 justify-center md:justify-start'>
            <a href="https://github.com/Joel-Moron" target="_blank"><img class='w-[35px]' src="/assets/logos/github.svg" alt="icono-github"></a>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/joel-moron-ochante-11342123b/" target="_blank"><img class='w-[35px]' src="/assets/logos/linkedin.svg" alt="icono-linkedin"></a>
            <a href={Curriculum} download><button class='border border-solid rounded-lg border-[#3b53a8] p-1 w-14 md:hidden'>CV</button></a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class='relative h-fit py-4 px-2 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-l from-[#18b9cfe6] to-[#002cc7]'>
        <img class='w-[250px] rounded-xl' src={Image.src} alt="Mi foto">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-[#22283126]"></div>
    </div>
</header>
